    "title": "feature request: non destructive prune switch",
    "body": "-prune option deletes blockchain files irreversibly.\r\nA switch (like -prune-keep-files for renaming the files instead of deleting would enable someone with a fully downloaded blockchain to create a trusted pruned node to copy onto other computers and thereafter revert to a full blockchain without first having to backup .bitcoin/blocks\r\n",
